movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Outstanding. Disney Star Wars Can't Compete With This
review: The soundtrack, the costume designs, the ships, the characters, the locations, podracers, duel of the fates, all are amazing. If you edit out the parts that drag, you get a masterpiece.

movie_title: Rogue One: A Star Wars Story
title: Epic, just needed more Vader massacres
review: The first real Star Wars movie since Revenge of the Sith. Love the locations. Asteroid planet, Coruscant, Jedha, Death Star, Scariff were all beautiful

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones
title: Beautiful Film. Epic Soundtrack. So Many Iconic Characters, Designs, Locations, Vehicles, Weapons, Music
review: This movie stood the test of time. Overwhelming detail crammed into every scene, sound effects top notch, great war sequences, deep lore etc...

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith
title: Best Star Wars Movie Ever Created
review:
Hands down the greatest movie created, in general. 
So much detail, overwhelming aesthetics, large scale battles, iconic characters, beautiful weapon/vehicle/planet designs. I love the cgi, it gives the prequels a futuristic vibe. Otherworldly. nice contrast to the grittiness of the OT

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode VII - The Force Awakens
title: I paid for a new SW movie, got A New Hope re-skinned
review: Did I just get scammed? I work hard for my money and YOU KNEW we would go see it day 1. The most anticipated sequel in HISTORY AND YOU GIVE US THIS

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode IV - A New Hope
title: No words to describe this movie.
review: It speaks for itself, wish there was a modern video game based on this and every movie except the sequel trilogy movies. That would be just epic.
